dcterms:description: DrugOOD is a systematic OOD dataset curator and benchmark for drug discovery, providing large-scale, realistic, and diverse datasets for graph OOD learning problems. It covers a wide range of shifts that naturally occur in molecular graphs, considering properties such as assay, molecular size, and molecular scaffold.
dcterms:title: DrugOOD

dcterms:description: GOOD is a systematic graph OOD benchmark that provides carefully designed data environments for distribution shifts, including covariate shift and concept shift, to evaluate OOD detection methods.
dcterms:title: GOOD
